<h3 id="уюІуюІgcnуџёУЙЊтЁЦТў»тЋЦ">уюІуюІGCNуџёУЙЊтЁЦТў»тЋЦ</h3>
<p>Given a graph $G = (V, E)$ , a GCN takes as input:</p>

<ul>
  <li>adjacency matrix $\mathbf{A}$ of $G$.   <em>N</em> ├Ќ <em>N</em></li>
  <li>an input feature matrix, $N ├Ќ FРЂ░$ feature matrix, $\mathbf{X}$,
    <ul>
      <li>where <em>N</em> is the number of nodes and</li>
      <li><em>FРЂ░</em> is the number of input features for each node</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

